    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escape From Benjamin's Room</strong> is a unique 2D puzzle adventure that will put your brain to work. You play as a stranger trapped in an old scientist's room who has lost his wife and wants to bring her back to life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras/b37a975dbaca9ff1ea4fe45b30dbe84d.avif?t=1751520282\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras_big/b37a975dbaca9ff1ea4fe45b30dbe84d.avif?t=1751520282 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think outside the box to solve all the puzzles in the room, click on any game objects to interact, and pay attention to the details</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras/2c5d769d78880f0b8e697fedfd574ae7.avif?t=1751520282\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras_big/2c5d769d78880f0b8e697fedfd574ae7.avif?t=1751520282 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put on your headphones to get immersed in this incredible escape room game. You'll enjoy this adventure to the fullest! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras/2aa1e51bea144acdaf75bbfa9b55e7b4.avif?t=1751520282\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras_big/2aa1e51bea144acdaf75bbfa9b55e7b4.avif?t=1751520282 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Besides the original Benjamin's room, you can play an Alternative room that has the same furniture, but different enigmas from the original room  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras/858fe631ab5f67a4b78a193751d2ffd9.avif?t=1751520282\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras_big/858fe631ab5f67a4b78a193751d2ffd9.avif?t=1751520282 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you enjoy solving logic problems and playing adventures like escape rooms or puzzle games, you will enjoy this adventure and put your brain to work.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras/7859b9e631c7e9a900868fd2c616fe7b.avif?t=1751520282\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras_big/7859b9e631c7e9a900868fd2c616fe7b.avif?t=1751520282 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you get stuck on solving <i>a</i> riddle, click the bulb button to get a hint that will help you solve the current enigma and escape the room.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras/f221e128dbdeaebe6f4bbf6c8f11e2ae.avif?t=1751520282\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras_big/f221e128dbdeaebe6f4bbf6c8f11e2ae.avif?t=1751520282 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong> here. I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing everything myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
